            <b>Browser-verified signals</b> supplement LLM-inferred DCP with machine-observed data:
          </p>
          <table cellpadding="3" cellspacing="2" style="font-size: var(--font-sm); margin-bottom: 0;">
            <tr>
              {['Tracking', 'Security', 'Accessibility', 'Consent'].map((el) => (
